                    <msContents>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                            <locus from="1ra" to="88ra"/>
                            <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1693John">Gospel of John</title>   
                            <note>A prefatory matter is given in the incipit</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">ብሥራተ፡ አብ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ትሩፍ፡ ረድእ፡ ተናጋሪ፡ በመለኮት፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ፍቁረ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ጸሎቱ፡ የሃሉ፡ ምስለ፡ 
                                <add>ፍቁሩ፡ <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14333QatsalaGiyorgis">ቀፀለ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡</persName></add></incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                            <locus from="88ra" to="90v"/>
                            <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2736RepCh20">Malkǝʾa Śǝllāse</title>
                            <note>The beginning is missing and the incipit starts ex abrupto in the 27th stanza.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez"><supplied reason="lost">ሰላም፡ ለእምታቲክሙ፡ መስፈርታተ፡ ም</supplied>ድር፡ ወሰማይ። 
                                አሠርግው<cb n="88rb"/>ኒ፡ ሥላሴ፡ በቀጠንተ፡ ምግባር፡ ሠናይ። 
                                ወረስዩኒ፡ ሐዳሰ፡ እምነ፡ ልማዱ፡ ብሉይ። 
                                ለባዕል፡ ዘተሣለቆ፡ ወዘተጓህለዎ፡ ንዋይ። 
                                እንዘ፡ በዴዴሁ፡ ይግዕር፡ እል<supplied reason="omitted">አ</supplied>ዛር፡ ድውይ። 
                                ሰላም፡ ለእራኃቲክሙ፡ እለ፡ አኃዛ፡ ዓለመ።</incipit>
                        </msItem>
                    </msContents>
